      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
          <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Î•Ï€ÎµÎ¾ÎµÏÎ³Î±ÏƒÎ¯Î± Î†ÏÎ¸ÏÎ¿Ï…</h1>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <a href={`/${article.lang}/blog/${article.slug}`} class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-500 text-white rounded hover:bg-gray-600 transition">ğŸ‘ï¸ Î ÏÎ¿ÎµÏ€Î¹ÏƒÎºÏŒÏ€Î·ÏƒÎ·</a>
            <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded hover:bg-blue-600 transition">â† Î Î¯ÏƒÏ‰</a>
